00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:40,640
'It doesn't really matter,' said 
Megan. 'We'll see him at the party.'

195
00:20:42,080 --> 00:20:47,440
Again, she was wrong. By the 
time they reached Goblin Valley,  

196
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:50,960
the car park was full and there 
was nowhere to stay for the night.

197
00:20:52,400 --> 00:20:58,640
The girls now felt very tired and decided 
not to go to the party. 'We'll drive to  

198
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:05,200
Little Wild Horse Canyon tomorrow morning,' 
