371
00:38:56,320 --> 00:39:04,000
police. The officer on the desk asked for Aron's 
information: full name, age, height and weight.  

372
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:09,200
He also wanted to know the model of 
his truck and the license-plate number.  

373
00:39:10,160 --> 00:39:14,880
But there was something the officer didn't 
